    <title>Mercury 13 legend Wally Funk will ride with Jeff Bezos to the edge of space</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KzPDkqEnsu8LTNOmwMLfeTLGWNs=/0x0:3520x2347/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/69528859/Blue_Origin_Wally_Funk.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Wally Funk in an undated photo provided by Blue Origin&lt;/figcaption&gt;
