  &lt;p id="t2eww3"&gt;A Florida internet law is on hold while a lawsuit contesting it continues. Judge Robert Hinkle has &lt;a href="https://storage.courtlistener.com/recap/gov.uscourts.flnd.371253/gov.uscourts.flnd.371253.113.0_1.pdf"&gt;issued a preliminary injunction&lt;/a&gt; blocking nearly all of SB 7072, a controversial and sweeping regulation of social media platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
